<title>FRANCE: Imetal 1996 sales up 4.8 percent.</title>
<headline>Imetal 1996 sales up 4.8 percent.</headline>
<dateline>PARIS 1997-01-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year to Dec 30, 1996.</p>
<p>(All figures in millions of French francs)</p>
<p>    Turnover					 8,109    vs    7,737</p>
<p>    - Construction materials		   2,790    vs    3,323</p>
<p>    - industrial minerals			3,130    vs    2,266</p>
<p>    - metal transformation		     2,189    vs    2,148</p>
<p>NOTE - The company said in a statement sales rose 4.8 percent during the year but on a like-for-like basis sales fell 0.2 percent. The group said the sales figures allowed it confirm 1996 net profits would rise by about 10 percent from 551 million francs last year.</p>
